{
  "stem": "24231.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they wanted me to play for them, so I got transferred.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was an opening in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Some of the guys went through the transport in-- into Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I came into that Home One.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's where I stayed all the time until the home was dissolved when everybody was shipped out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was the only one who stayed in the-- in the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And what I did, I-- I-- then I had to get a job.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Most of the guys in the home, they work in the-- some of them were plumbers, repairing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They had all kinds of odd jobs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They worked in the fields, in the gardens.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- and I-- I wanted to-- I had an opportunity in the home to get some education.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because the-- the-- the leaders, the guys who were in charge of these individuals previously were professors.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was a Professor Eisinger who was-- who was from Moravia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He was from Professor Swicker, who was from the University of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And another-- there was a Professor Cohn, who was a mathematician.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So these guys said, well, you know, you guys let's get take a chance.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we're going to start a schools.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So we-- we had-- some of the kids in the morning went to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They had school in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Some of them went to work in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They-- they had classes in the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And any time we had some kind of a visit from-- from the SS man, and so you know everybody-- there was always a guard outside the way watching, so nobody would-- so we wouldn't get surprised or the books wouldn't be visible.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Because we couldn't-- we could--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These were secret schools, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they weren't permitted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were secret schools.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
